{"type":"message","id":"92bdb56a","parentId":"816153fc","timestamp":"2026-04-07T10:30:37.983Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"从日志分析来看，**问题不是出在 OpenClaw 配置，而是出在你的本地 GPU 服务端 llama.cpp 这边**：\n\n## 🔍 问题诊断\n\n**根本原因：**\n你本地加载 `qwen3.5-35b-a3b` 模型时，llama.cpp 只分配了 **4096** 的上下文窗口 (`n_ctx=4096`)，但 OpenClaw 的系统提示 + 会话上下文已经占用了 13464 tokens，超过了模型能处理的最大长度。\n\n```\nError: The number of tokens to keep from the initial prompt is greater than the context length\n(n_keep: 13464 >= n_ctx: 4096)\n```\n\n**OpenClaw 配置看起来是对的：**\n你的配置里 `contextWindow: 262144`（256k），这没问题。问题出在服务端实际加载模型时上下文参数太小。\n\n## 🛠️ 解决方法\n\n你需要修改 llama.cpp 启动脚本/命令行参数，增加 `--ctx-size` 参数：\n\n**正确启动示例：**\n```bash\n./server -m models/qwen3.5-35b-a3b.gguf --port 12345 --ctx-size 262144\n```\n\n关键参数就是 `--ctx-size 262144`，把上下文窗口改大。\n\n---\n\n另外我顺便把 OpenClaw 缺失的 npm 依赖都给你补上了，之前 CLI 启动都报错，现在正常了。改完模型上下文重启一下本地服务和 OpenClaw gateway 就好了。\n\n你现在用的是哪个服务端？llama.cpp 还是别的？"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"custom-ark-cn-beijing-volces-com","model":"ark-code-latest","usage":{"input":22154,"output":392,"cacheRead":3896,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":26442,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775557830137,"responseId":"0217755578302658e13156721812cf3aa873c08415dc3f48b408a"}}
