{"type":"message","id":"680a5f64","parentId":"73830b0f","timestamp":"2026-04-07T10:33:15.303Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"问题很清楚了，**错误还是一样的**：\n\n```\nThe number of tokens to keep from the initial prompt is greater than the context length \n(n_keep: 18320 >= n_ctx: 4096)\n```\n\n虽然你改了 OpenClaw 配置里的 `contextWindow`，但 **llama.cpp 服务端加载模型时仍然只分配了 4096 的上下文**，问题根本没有解决。\n\n你是怎么启动 llama.cpp server 的？把你的启动命令或者脚本给我看一下。要在**启动服务的时候**加上 `--ctx-size 131072` 或者更大的参数才行。\n\n---\n\n顺便说一下，`n_keep` 已经到 18k+ 了，即使开 128k（131072）也完全足够。"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"custom-ark-cn-beijing-volces-com","model":"ark-code-latest","usage":{"input":6195,"output":190,"cacheRead":18232,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":24617,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775557992253,"responseId":"02177555799238670efbf1cf5c1ae3d0b3f284807454d29bf3b1a"}}
{"type":"compaction","id":"0c02415b","parentId":"680a5f64","timestamp":"2026-04-07T10:33:54.009Z","summary":"## Goal\n排查本地模型 `local-gpu/qwen3.5-35b-a3b` 调用不通的问题，通过查看日志定位原因；用户修改配置后测试修改后的模型是否能正常调用。\n\n## Constraints & Preferences\n- (none)\n\n## Progress\n### Done\n- 定位问题根源：OpenClaw 的 Node.js 依赖存在大量缺失，导致CLI无法正常启动读取配置\n- 手动全局安装了缺失的 `@buape/carbon`、`@larksuiteoapi/node-sdk`、`@slack/web-api` 三个依赖\n- 在OpenClaw的Homebrew安装目录重新执行完整的 `npm install`，成功安装所有依赖，解决依赖缺失问题，OpenClaw日志可以正常查看\n- 执行日志查看命令，获取到了日志开头内容\n- 读取 `/Users/liuchenglong/.openclaw/workspace/MEMORY.md` 文件获取上下文\n- 分析OpenClaw日志，定位出 `local-gpu/qwen3.5-35b-a3b` 模型调用失败的具体原因\n- 补上了OpenClaw缺失的npm依赖，修复了CLI启动报错问题\n- 用户修改模型上下文参数并重启服务后，已经发起了测试会话，测试修改后的模型是否能正常调用\n\n### In Progress\n- [ ] 等待测试会话的结果返回，确认模型是否恢复正常\n\n### Blocked\n- (none)\n\n## Key Decisions\n- **在OpenClaw的Homebrew安装目录重新执行完整 `npm install`**: 解决全局安装单个依赖仍无法覆盖所有缺失依赖的问题 (rationale: 依赖缺失导致CLI无法启动)\n- **修改本地llama.cpp服务端的模型启动参数，增加`--ctx-size 262144`**: 解决模型实际加载时上下文窗口小于实际需求token数的问题 (rationale: 错误显示`n_keep: 13464 >= n_ctx: 4096`，OpenClaw配置的上下文窗口正确，问题出在服务端加载参数)\n\n## Next Steps\n1. 等待测试会话完成并获取结果，确认模型是否可以正常调用\n2. 根据测试结果给出最终结论\n\n## Critical Context\n- Session initialized on Tuesday, April 7th, 2026 — 6:21 PM (Asia/Shanghai) / 2026-04-07 10:21 UTC\n- User has sent a greeting in Chinese: \"你好\"\n- Current context label/id: openclaw-control-ui\n- 目标模型ID: `local-gpu/qwen3.5-35b-a3b`\n- 已读取上下文文件: `/Users/liuchenglong/.openclaw/workspace/MEMORY.md`\n- 模型调用失败的根本原因：本地llama.cpp加载模型时分配的上下文窗口为`n_ctx=4096`，但OpenClaw系统提示+会话上下文已占用13464 tokens，超过模型处理上限，报错信息：`The number of tokens to keep from the initial prompt is greater than the context length (n_keep: 13464 >= n_ctx: 4096). Try to load the model with a larger context length, or provide a shorter input.`\n- OpenClaw配置中该模型的`contextWindow: 262144`配置正确，问题出在llama.cpp服务端的启动参数\n- 已生成测试子会话，ID为`agent:main:subagent:497a886b-e16f-484a-af14-bde1fdfbf86c`，运行ID为`cf628654-df9d-41c3-9032-b1bfe939ce07`，等待测试结果返回\n\n---\n\n**Turn Context (split turn):**\n\n## Original Request\nA completed subagent task was ready for delivery: the task was to test if the local model `local-gpu/qwen3.5-35b-a3b` can be called normally by sending a simple greeting request, and confirm if it can reply successfully. The subagent result had no output with 0 total tokens, and the assistant needed to diagnose the issue.\n\n## Early Progress\n1.  The assistant confirmed the test failed (0 runtime, 0 tokens) and began checking logs\n2.  First two attempts to retrieve logs failed (default log path did not exist, incorrect `openclaw` command syntax)\n3.  Ran `openclaw gateway status` to get correct service information, confirmed gateway is running correctly and found the correct log file path: `/tmp/openclaw/openclaw-2026-04-07.log`\n4.  Ran the tail command to get the latest 100 lines of the log, and the truncated output starts showing log entries\n\n## Context for Suffix\n- The test of the local model `qwen3.5-35b-a3b` failed to produce any output\n- The truncated log already shows one clear error: the number of tokens to keep from the initial prompt (18322) exceeds the model's configured context length (4096)\n- The retained suffix is the continuation of this pulled log content\n\n<read-files>\n/Users/liuchenglong/.openclaw/workspace/MEMORY.md\n</read-files>","firstKeptEntryId":"680a5f64","tokensBefore":24617,"details":{"readFiles":["/Users/liuchenglong/.openclaw/workspace/MEMORY.md"],"modifiedFiles":[]},"fromHook":false}
