de_modules/openclaw/dist/subsystem-CJEvHE2o.js:279:46\",\"fileName\":\"subsystem-CJEvHE2o.js\",\"fileNameWithLine\":\"subsystem-CJEvHE2o.js:279\",\"fileColumn\":\"46\",\"fileLine\":\"279\",\"filePath\":\"Users/liuchenglong/.nvm/versions/node/v23.11.1/lib/node_modules/openclaw/dist/subsystem-CJEvHE2o.js\",\"filePathWithLine\":\"Users/liuchenglong/.nvm/versions/node/v23.11.1/lib/node_modules/openclaw/dist/subsystem-CJEvHE2o.js:279\"}},\"time\":\"2026-04-07T18:33:15.382+08:00\"}\n{\"0\":\"问题很清楚了，**错误还是一样的**：\\n\\n```\\nThe number of tokens to keep from the initial prompt is greater than the context length \\n(n_keep: 18320 >= n_ctx: 4096)\\n```\\n\\n虽然你改了 OpenClaw 配置里的 `contextWindow`，但 **llama.cpp 服务端加载模型时仍然只分配了 4096 的上下文**，问题根本没有解决。\\n\\n你是怎么启动 llama.cpp server 的？把你的启动命令或者脚本给我看一下。要在**启动服务的时候**加上 `--ctx-size 131072` 或者更大的参数才行。\\n\\n---\\n\\n顺便说一下，`n_keep` 已经到 18k+ 了，即使开 128k（131072）也完全足够。\",\"_meta\":{\"runtime\":\"node\",\"runtimeVersion\":\"25.9.0\",\"hostname\":\"unknown\",\"name\":\"openclaw\",\"date\":\"2026-04-07T10:33:15.382Z\",\"logLevelId\":3,\"logLevelName\":\"INFO\",\"path\":{\"fullFilePath\":\"file:///Users/liuchenglong/.nvm/versions/node/v23.11.1/lib/node_modules/openclaw/dist/subsystem-CJEvHE2o.js:279:46\",\"fileName\":\"subsystem-CJEvHE2o.js\",\"fileNameWithLine\":\"subsystem-CJEvHE2o.js:279\",\"fileColumn\":\"46\",\"fileLine\":\"279\",\"filePath\":\"Users/liuchenglong/.nvm/versions/node/v23.11.1/lib/node_modules/openclaw/dist/subsystem-CJEvHE2o.js\",\"filePathWithLine\":\"Users/liuchenglong/.nvm/versions/node/v23.11.1/lib/node_modules/openclaw/dist/subsystem-CJEvHE2o.js:279\"}},\"time\":\"2026-04-07T18:33:15.382+08:00\"}\n{\"0\":\"{\\\"subsystem\\\":\\\"agent/embedded\\\"}\",\"1\":\"low context window: custom-ark-cn-beijing-volces-com/ark-code-latest ctx=16000 (warn<32000) source=modelsConfig\",\"_meta\":{\"runtime\":\"node\",\"runtimeVersion\":\"25.9.0\",\"hostname\":\"unknown\",\"name\":\"{\\\"subsystem\\\":\\\"agent/embedded\\\"}\",\"parentNames\":[