{"type":"message","id":"38f7a00e","parentId":"eec2ccff","timestamp":"2026-04-07T10:36:18.930Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"找到了！问题在这里：\n\n```json\n\"local-gpu\": {\n  \"baseUrl\": \"http://112.226.133.33:12345/v1\",\n  \"api\": \"openai-responses\",  // ❌ 错误！\n  ...\n}\n```\n\n你远程 llama.cpp server 暴露的是标准的 **OpenAI 兼容 `/chat/completions` API**，但是你配置成了 `api: \"openai-responses\"`，这是 OpenAI 新出的 Responses API，格式完全不一样！\n\n所以 OpenClaw 发错了请求格式，远程服务器解析失败，实际根本没处理请求，模型还是用默认配置跑？不对... 等等，报错里的 `n_keep: 18322 >= n_ctx: 4096` 明明就是 llama.cpp server 自己返回的错误！\n\n那我们再看看，API 地址对不对？\n\n你给的是 `http://112.226.133.33:12345/api/v1/models`，但配置里是 `baseUrl: \"http://112.226.133.33:12345/v1\"`，应该改成 `baseUrl: \"http://112.226.133.33:12345/api\"` 才对！\n\n然后 API 格式应该是 `openai`（标准 `/chat/completions`），不是 `openai-responses`！\n\n改完这两处就对了。让我现在给你打补丁：\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_tjifm3a1y15ytdkd68v2cw0q","name":"gateway","arguments":{"action":"config.patch","patch":{"models":{"providers":{"local-gpu":{"baseUrl":"http://112.226.133.33:12345/api","api":"openai"}}}},"note":"修复 local-gpu 提供商配置：修正 baseUrl 路径为 /api，并将 API 格式从错误的 openai-responses 改为标准 openai (兼容 llama.cpp server)"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"custom-ark-cn-beijing-volces-com","model":"ark-code-latest","usage":{"input":5657,"output":503,"cacheRead":20792,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":26952,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775558170549,"responseId":"021775558170676f9065cef9012c43073e2d0226029aed4c5de8e"}}
